article_id:2082,category_name:News,title_name:The Stamina Cost of Certain Quests Will Be Adjusted,image_path:,message:<div>The stamina cost of certain quests will be reduced as part of an update in late April.</div><div><br></div><div>Please note that this change does not affect the amount of stamina recovered from the 30-Day Pack (Recovery) or from the use of wyrmite or honey, nor does it affect the type, amount, or rate of drop rewards.</div><div><br></div><div>Further details will be provided in an upcoming notification.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1616824800,update_time1616747738